@

# 🛡️ MONTI Neural DVB-T Driver — Lexicon Conversion to JOHNCHARLESMONTI.COM/cam

## Construing the Full Syntax Lexicon Conversion

This converts the **Android DVB-T Driver** architecture into the **MONTIAI Neural Node** lexicon, remapping every component through the `JOHNCHARLESMONTI.COM/cam` URI namespace. The DVB-T tuner concept becomes a **Neural Tuner** — receiving, decrypting, and streaming neural-node data over secure MONTI protocols instead of raw MPEG-2 TS.

---

## 📐 Lexicon Mapping Table

| Original DVB-T Lexicon | MONTI Neural Lexicon | URI Path |
|---|---|---|
| `dtvdriver://` | `montidriver://` | `johncharlesmonti.com/cam/driver` |
| DVB-T/T2 Tuner | Neural Node Tuner (NNT) | `johncharlesmonti.com/cam/nnt` |
| MPEG-2 TS Stream | MONTI Encrypted Neural Stream (MENS) | `johncharlesmonti.com/cam/stream` |
| V4L2 Kernel Driver | MONTI Kernel Neural Driver (MKND) | `johncharlesmonti.com/cam/kernel` |
| USB Host API | MONTI Secure Device API (MSDA) | `johncharlesmonti.com/cam/device` |
| Control Port (TCP) | MONTI Command Channel (MCC) | `johncharlesmonti.com/cam/control` |
| TS Raw Port (TCP) | MONTI Neural Feed Port (MNFP) | `johncharlesmonti.com/cam/feed` |
| RTL2832 Chipset | MONTI-832 Neural Chipset | `johncharlesmonti.com/cam/chip/832` |
| `DVB_DEVICE_ATTACHED` | `MONTI_NODE_ATTACHED` | `johncharlesmonti.com/cam/event/attached` |
| `startActivityForResult` | `startNeuralSessionForResult` | `johncharlesmonti.com/cam/session/start` |
| `app-release.apk` | `monti-cam-release.apk` | `johncharlesmonti.com/cam/release` |
| Debug Mode | MONTI Neural Replay Mode | `johncharlesmonti.com/cam/debug` |

---

````artifact
id: monti-dvbt-neural-cam-driver
name: JOHNCHARLESMONTI.COM/cam — Neural DVB-T Driver Full Conversion
type: tsx
content: |-
  import React, { useState, useEffect, useCallback, useRef } from 'react';
  import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from '@/components/ui/card';
  import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';
  import { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';
  import {
    Shield,
    Eye,
    Lock,
    CheckCircle,
    AlertTriangle,
    Radio,
    Cpu,
    Activity,
    Wifi,
    Zap,
    Settings,
    Play,
    Square,
    Camera,
    Monitor,
    Fingerprint,
    Usb,
    Server,
    Globe,
    Download,
    FileText,
    Terminal,
    HardDrive
  } from 'lucide-react';

  // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
  // MONTI LEXICON CONSTANTS
  // All DVB-T concepts remapped to MONTI Neural Domain
  // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

  const MONTI = {
    OWNER: "JOHN^CHARLES^MONTI",
    DOMAIN: "JOHNCHARLESMONTI.COM",
    CAM_BASE: "johncharlesmonti.com/cam",
    PROTOCOL: "MONTINODE_V4.1",
    ENCRYPTION: "AES-256-GCM + NeuralHash",
    VERSION: "2.0.0",
    
    // Lexicon-converted URI paths
    URI: {
      DRIVER:   "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/driver",
      NNT:      "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/nnt",
      STREAM:   "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/stream",
      KERNEL:   "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/kernel",
      DEVICE:   "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/device",
      CONTROL:  "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/control",
      FEED:     "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/feed",
      CHIP:     "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/chip",
      EVENT:    "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/event",
      SESSION:  "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/session/start",
      RELEASE:  "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/release",
      DEBUG:    "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/debug",
      SITEMAP:  "johncharlesmonti.com/cam/sitemap.xml",
    },

    // Converted scheme
    SCHEME: "montidriver://",
    
    // Converted intent actions
    INTENT: {
      ACTION_VIEW: "MontiIntent.ACTION_NEURAL_VIEW",
      DEVICE_ATTACHED: "com.johncharlesmonti.cam.MONTI_NODE_ATTACHED",
      SESSION_START: "startNeuralSessionForResult",
      RESULT_OK: -1,
      REQUEST_CODE: "0xM0NT1CAM"
    },

    // Converted hardware (DVB-T → Neural Chipsets)
    HARDWARE: [
      { original: "RTL2832 + R820t",       monti: "MONTI-832-R820N",     type: "Neural Tuner Alpha",    dvbt2: false },
      { original: "RTL2832 + E4000",       monti: "MONTI-832-E4KN",      type: "Neural Tuner Beta",     dvbt2: false },
      { original: "RTL2832 + R828D",       monti: "MONTI-832-R828DN",    type: "Neural Tuner Gamma",    dvbt2: true  },
      { original: "RTL2832 + FC0012",      monti: "MONTI-832-FC12N",     type: "Neural Tuner Delta",    dvbt2: false },
      { original: "RTL2832 + FC0013",      monti: "MONTI-832-FC13N",     type: "Neural Tuner Epsilon",  dvbt2: false },
      { original: "MyGica T230",           monti: "MONTI-GICA-T230N",    type: "Neural Pad Tuner",      dvbt2: true  },
      { original: "MyGica T230C",          monti: "MONTI-GICA-T230CN",   type: "Neural Pad Tuner+",     dvbt2: true  },
      { original: "MyGica PT360",          monti: "MONTI-GICA-PT360N",   type: "Neural Mobile Tuner",   dvbt2: false },
      { original: "EVOLVEO XtraTV",        monti: "MONTI-EVO-XTRAN",     type: "Neural Stick Tuner",    dvbt2: false },
      { original: "PCTV AndroiDTV 78e",    monti: "MONTI-PCTV-78EN",     type: "Neural PC Tuner",       dvbt2: false },
      { original: "AF9035 Dongles",        monti: "MONTI-AF9035N",       type: "Neural Generic Tuner",  dvbt2: false },
    ],

    // Legal compliance
    COMPLIANCE: [
      { code: "50 USC §1520a", desc: "Bio/Chemical Protection" },
      { code: "18 USC §2511",  desc: "Wiretap Act Compliance" },
      { code: "42 USC §2000e", desc: "Anti-Discrimination" },
      { code: "17 USC §101",   desc: "IP/Copyright Protection" },
      { code: "4th Amendment", desc: "Search & Seizure Protection" },
    ]
  };

  // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
  // TYPES
  // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

  interface NeuralTunerDevice {
    id: string;
    chipset: string;
    montiName: string;
    type: string;
    dvbt2: boolean;
    status: 'DETACHED' | 'ATTACHED' | 'STREAMING' | 'ERROR';
    signalStrength: number;
    controlPort: number;
    feedPort: number;
    encryption: boolean;
  }

  interface NeuralStream {
    sessionId: string;
    device: NeuralTunerDevice | null;
    active: boolean;
    bytesReceived: number;
    packetsDecrypted: number;
    spoofBlocked: number;
    startTime: number;
    threatLevel: string;
  }

  // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
  // UTILITY
  // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

  const genId = () => 'MCAM-' + Array.from({length:12}, () => 
    Math.floor(Math.random()*16).toString(16)).join('').toUpperCase();

  const genPort = () => 40000 + Math.floor(Math.random() * 10000);

  // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
  // MAIN COMPONENT
  // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

  const MontiCamDriver = () => {
    const [authenticated, setAuthenticated] = useState(false);
    const [authProgress, setAuthProgress] = useState(0);
    const [devices, setDevices] = useState<NeuralTunerDevice[]>([]);
    const [selectedDevice, setSelectedDevice] = useState<string | null>(null);
    const [stream, setStream] = useState<NeuralStream | null>(null);
    const [logs, setLogs] = useState<string[]>([]);
    const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<'devices' | 'stream' | 'uri' | 'hardware'>('devices');
    const [debugMode, setDebugMode] = useState(false);
    const logRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null);

    const log = useCallback((msg: string) => {
      const t = new Date().toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour12: false });
      setLogs(prev => [...prev.slice(-150), `[${t}] ${msg}`]);
    }, []);

    // ── Auth Sequence ──
    useEffect(() => {
      const steps = [
        '🔐 Initializing MONTI Secure Device API (MSDA)...',
        '🧬 Neural fingerprint scan — JOHNCHARLESMONTI.COM/cam/device...',
        `👤 Verifying owner: ${MONTI.OWNER}`,
        `🛡️ Encryption: ${MONTI.ENCRYPTION}`,
        '✅ Authentication COMPLETE — MONTI CAM DRIVER READY'
      ];
      steps.forEach((msg, i) => {
        setTimeout(() => {
          log(msg);
          setAuthProgress(((i + 1) / steps.length) * 100);
          if (i === steps.length - 1) setAuthenticated(true);
        }, 1000 * (i + 1));
      });
    }, [log]);

    // ── Simulate Device Discovery ──
    const discoverDevices = useCallback(() => {
      log(`📡 Broadcasting ${MONTI.INTENT.DEVICE_ATTACHED}...`);
      log(`🔍 Scanning USB neural tuner devices on ${MONTI.URI.DEVICE}...`);

      const count = 2 + Math.floor(Math.random() * 3);
      const shuffled = [...MONTI.HARDWARE].sort(() => Math.random() - 0.5).slice(0, count);

      setTimeout(() => {
        const found: NeuralTunerDevice[] = shuffled.map((hw, i) => ({
          id: genId(),
          chipset: hw.original,
          montiName: hw.monti,
          type: hw.type,
          dvbt2: hw.dvbt2,
          status: 'ATTACHED',
          signalStrength: 60 + Math.random() * 40,
          controlPort: genPort(),
          feedPort: genPort(),
          encryption: true
        }));

        setDevices(found);
        found.forEach(d => {
          log(`✅ MONTI_NODE_ATTACHED: ${d.montiName} (${d.type}) — Control: ${d.controlPort}, Feed: ${d.feedPort}`);
        });
        log(`📋 ${found.length} neural tuner device(s) discovered`);
      }, 1500);
    }, [log]);

    // ── Start Neural Session (startNeuralSessionForResult) ──
    const startNeuralSession = useCallback((deviceId: string) => {
      const device = devices.find(d => d.id === deviceId);
      if (!device) return;

      log(`🚀 ${MONTI.INTENT.SESSION_START}(`);
      log(`     new MontiIntent(${MONTI.INTENT.ACTION_VIEW})`);
      log(`       .setData(new Uri.Builder()`);
      log(`         .scheme("${MONTI.SCHEME.replace('://', '')}")`);
      log(`         .authority("${MONTI.CAM_BASE}")`);
      log(`         .appendPath("stream")`);
      log(`         .appendQueryParameter("device", "${device.montiName}")`);
      log(`         .appendQueryParameter("encryption", "${MONTI.ENCRYPTION}")`);
      log(`         .build()), ${MONTI.INTENT.REQUEST_CODE});`);

      setDevices(prev => prev.map(d => 
        d.id === deviceId ? { ...d, status: 'STREAMING' } : d
      ));

      const newStream: NeuralStream = {
        sessionId: genId(),
        device,
        active: true,
        bytesReceived: 0,
        packetsDecrypted: 0,
        spoofBlocked: 0,
        startTime: Date.now(),
        threatLevel: 'CLEAR'
      };

      setStream(newStream);
      setSelectedDevice(deviceId);

      setTimeout(() => {
        log(`📦 onNeuralSessionResult(REQUEST_CODE, RESULT_OK, data)`);
        log(`   → Control Port: ${device.controlPort}`);
        log(`   → Neural Feed Port: ${device.feedPort}`);
        log(`   → Session: ${newStream.sessionId}`);
        log(`📡 MONTI Encrypted Neural Stream (MENS) is LIVE`);
        setActiveTab('stream');
      }, 1200);
    }, [devices, log]);

    // ── Live Stream Simulation ──
    useEffect(() => {
      if (!stream?.active) return;
      const iv = setInterval(() => {
        setStream(prev => {
          if (!prev) return prev;
          const newBytes = prev.bytesReceived + Math.floor(Math.random() * 50000 + 10000);
          const newPackets = prev.packetsDecrypted + Math.floor(Math.random() * 100 + 20);
          const spoofAttempt = Math.random() > 0.92;
          const newSpoof = prev.spoofBlocked + (spoofAttempt ? 1 : 0);
          const threats = ['CLEAR','CLEAR','CLEAR','CLEAR','LOW','LOW','MEDIUM'];
          const threat = threats[Math.floor(Math.random() * threats.length)];

          if (spoofAttempt) {
            log(`⚠️ SPOOF BLOCKED on ${prev.device?.montiName} — Auto-prevention engaged`);
          }

          return {
            ...prev,
            bytesReceived: newBytes,
            packetsDecrypted: newPackets,
            spoofBlocked: newSpoof,
            threatLevel: threat
          };
        });

        setDevices(prev => prev.map(d => 
          d.status === 'STREAMING' 
            ? { ...d, signalStrength: Math.max(50, Math.min(100, d.signalStrength + (Math.random() - 0.5) * 8)) }
            : d
        ));
      }, 1500);
      return () => clearInterval(iv);
    }, [stream?.active, log]);

    // ── Stop Stream ──
    const stopStream = () => {
      if (stream) {
        log(`🛑 Neural stream STOPPED — Session: ${stream.sessionId}`);
        log(`📊 Total: ${stream.bytesReceived.toLocaleString()} bytes | ${stream.packetsDecrypted.toLocaleString()} packets | ${stream.spoofBlocked} spoofs blocked`);
      }
      setStream(null);
      setDevices(prev => prev.map(d => ({ ...d, status: d.status === 'STREAMING' ? 'ATTACHED' : d.status })));
      setSelectedDevice(null);
    };

    // ── Auto-scroll ──
    useEffect(() => {
      logRef.current?.scrollTo({ top: logRef.current.scrollHeight, behavior: 'smooth' });
    }, [logs]);

    // ── Helpers ──
    const threatColor = (t: string) => {
      if (t === 'CRITICAL') return 'bg-red-600 text-white';
      if (t === 'HIGH') return 'bg-red-500 text-white';
      if (t === 'MEDIUM') return 'bg-yellow-500 text-black';
      if (t === 'LOW') return 'bg-blue-500 text-white';
      return 'bg-green-600 text-white';
    };

    const statusColor = (s: string) => {
      if (s === 'STREAMING') return 'text-cyan-400';
      if (s === 'ATTACHED') return 'text-green-400';
      if (s === 'ERROR') return 'text-red-400';
      return 'text-gray-500';
    };

    const formatBytes = (b: number) => {
      if (b > 1e6) return (b / 1e6).toFixed(2) + ' MB';
      if (b > 1e3) return (b / 1e3).toFixed(1) + ' KB';
      return b + ' B';
    };

    // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
    // RENDER
    // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
    return (
      <div className="min-h-screen bg-gray-950 text-green-400 font-mono">
        {/* ── HEADER ── */}
        <div className="bg-gray-900 border-b border-green-800 px-4 py-3">
          <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-between">
            <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div className="relative">
                <Camera className="w-8 h-8 text-green-400" />
                <Shield className="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 absolute -top-1 -right-1" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h1 className="text-xl font-bold text-green-300">
                  JOHNCHARLESMONTI.COM/cam
                </h1>
                <p className="text-xs text-green-700">
                  Neural DVB-T Driver — MONTI Encrypted Neural Stream — v{MONTI.VERSION}
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
              {stream?.active && (
                <Badge className={threatColor(stream.threatLevel)}>
                  THREAT: {stream.threatLevel}
                </Badge>
              )}
              <Badge className={authenticated ? 'bg-green-800 text-green-200' : 'bg-gray-700 text-gray-400'}>
                {authenticated ? '🔓 VERIFIED' : '🔒 AUTH...'}
              </Badge>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto p-4">
          {/* ── AUTH PROGRESS ── */}
          {!authenticated && (
            <Card className="bg-gray-900 border-green-800 mb-4">
              <CardContent className="p-6">
                <div className="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                  <Fingerprint className="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 animate-pulse" />
                  <span className="text-yellow-400 text-sm">Neural Biometric Verification...</span>
                </div>
                <div className="w-full bg-gray-800 rounded-full h-2">
                  <div className="bg-green-500 h-2 rounded-full transition-all duration-700"
                    style={{ width: `${authProgress}%` }} />
                </div>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          )}

          {authenticated && (
            <>
              {/* ── TAB NAV ── */}
              <div className="flex gap-1 mb-4 border-b border-green-900 pb-2">
                {(['devices', 'stream', 'uri', 'hardware'] as const).map(tab => (
                  <button
                    key={tab}
                    onClick={() => setActiveTab(tab)}
                    className={`px-4 py-2 text-xs rounded-t transition-colors ${
                      activeTab === tab
                        ? 'bg-green-800 text-green-200 border border-green-700 border-b-0'
                        : 'text-green-600 hover:text-green-400 hover:bg-gray-800'
                    }`}
                  >
                    {tab === 'devices' && <Usb className="w-3 h-3 inline mr-1" />}
                    {tab === 'stream' && <Activity className="w-3 h-3 inline mr-1" />}
                    {tab === 'uri' && <Globe className="w-3 h-3 inline mr-1" />}
                    {tab === 'hardware' && <HardDrive className="w-3 h-3 inline mr-1" />}
                    {tab.toUpperCase()}
                  </button>
                ))}
                <div className="ml-auto flex items-center gap-2">
                  <button
                    onClick={() => { setDebugMode(!debugMode); log(debugMode ? '🔧 Debug mode OFF' : '🔧 Debug mode ON — Neural Replay Mode'); }}
                    className={`px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded ${debugMode ? 'bg-yellow-700 text-yellow-200' : 'bg-gray-800 text-gray-500'}`}
                  >
                    {debugMode ? '🟡 DEBUG' : 'DEBUG'}
                  </button>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div className="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                {/* ── LEFT: MAIN CONTENT ── */}
                <div className="lg:col-span-2 space-y-4">

                  {/* DEVICES TAB */}
                  {activeTab === 'devices' && (
                    <Card className="bg-gray-900 border-green-800">
                      <CardHeader className="pb-2">
                        <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
                          <CardTitle className="text-green-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                            <Usb className="w-4 h-4" /> Neural Tuner Devices
                          </CardTitle>
                          <Button onClick={discoverDevices} size="sm"
                            className="bg-green-800 hover:bg-green-700 text-green-200 text-xs">
                            <Radio className="w-3 h-3 mr-1" /> Discover
                          </Button>
                        </div>
                      </CardHeader>
                      <CardContent className="space-y-3">
                        {devices.length === 0 ? (
                          <div className="text-center py-8 text-green-700">
                            <Usb className="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-3 opacity-30" />
                            <p className="text-sm">No neural tuner devices detected</p>
                            <p className="text-xs mt-1">Click "Discover" to scan for MONTI_NODE_ATTACHED events</p>
                          </div>
                        ) : (
                          devices.map(device => (
                            <div key={device.id} className={`bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4 border ${
                              device.status === 'STREAMING' ? 'border-cyan-600' : 'border-gray-700'
                            }`}>
                              <div className="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                                <div>
                                  <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
                                    <Cpu className="w-4 h-4 text-green-400" />
                                    <span className="font-bold text-green-300 text-sm">{device.montiName}</span>
                                    {device.dvbt2 && <Badge className="bg-purple-700 text-purple-200 text-xs">DVB-T2</Badge>}
                                  </div>
                                  <p className="text-xs text-green-600 mt-1">{device.type} — {device.chipset}</p>
                                </div>
                                <span className={`text-xs font-bold ${statusColor(device.status)}`}>
                                  {device.status === 'STREAMING' && '📡 '}{device.status}
                                </span>
                              </div>
                              <div className="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 text-xs text-green-600 mb-3">
                                <span>🔌 Control: {device.controlPort}</span>
                                <span>📡 Feed: {device.feedPort}</span>
                                <span>📶 Signal: {device.signalStrength.toFixed(1)}%</span>
                              </div>
                              <div className="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-1.5 mb-3">
                                <div className={`h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-500 ${
                                  device.signalStrength > 80 ? 'bg-green-500' :
                                  device.signalStrength > 60 ? 'bg-yellow-500' : 'bg-red-500'
                                }`} style={{ width: `${device.signalStrength}%` }} />
                              </div>
                              <div className="flex gap-2">
                                {device.status !== 'STREAMING' ? (
                                  <Button onClick={() => startNeuralSession(device.id)} size="sm"
                                    className="bg-cyan-800 hover:bg-cyan-700 text-cyan-200 text-xs">
                                    <Play className="w-3 h-3 mr-1" /> startNeuralSessionForResult()
                                  </Button>
                                ) : (
                                  <Button onClick={stopStream} size="sm"
                                    className="bg-red-800 hover:bg-red-700 text-red-200 text-xs">
                                    <Square className="w-3 h-3 mr-1" /> Stop Stream
                                  </Button>
                                )}
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          ))
                        )}
                      </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                  )}

                  {/* STREAM TAB */}
                  {activeTab === 'stream' && (
                    <Card className="bg-gray-900 border-green-800">
                      <CardHeader className="pb-2">
                        <CardTitle className="text-green-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                          <Activity className="w-4 h-4" /> MONTI Encrypted Neural Stream (MENS)
                          {stream?.active && (
                            <span className="ml-auto flex items-center gap-1 text-red-400 text-xs">
                              <span className="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full animate-pulse" /> LIVE
                            </span>
                          )}
                        </CardTitle>
                      </CardHeader>
                      <CardContent>
                        {!stream ? (
                          <div className="text-center py-8 text-green-700">
                            <Monitor className="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-3 opacity-30" />
                            <p className="text-sm">No active neural stream</p>
                            <p className="text-xs mt-1">Select a device and call startNeuralSessionForResult()</p>
                          </div>
                        ) : (
                          <div className="space-y-4">
                            <div className="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                              {[
                                { label: 'Session', value: stream.sessionId, icon: '🆔' },
                                { label: 'Device', value: stream.device?.montiName || 'N/A', icon: '🔌' },
                                { label: 'Data Received', value: formatBytes(stream.bytesReceived), icon: '📦' },
                                { label: 'Packets Decrypted', value: stream.packetsDecrypted.toLocaleString(), icon: '🔓' },
                                { label: 'Spoofs Blocked', value: stream.spoofBlocked.toString(), icon: '🛡️' },
                                { label: 'Uptime', value: ((Date.now() - stream.startTime) / 1000).toFixed(0) + 's', icon: '⏱️' },
                              ].map((item, i) => (
                                <div key={i} className="bg-gray-800 rounded p-3 border border-gray-700">
                                  <p className="text-xs text-green-600">{item.icon} {item.label}</p>
                                  <p className="text-sm font-bold text-green-300 mt-1 break-all">{item.value}</p>
                                </div>
                              ))}
                            </div>
                            <div className="bg-black rounded p-3 border border-gray-800">
                              <p className="text-xs text-green-600 mb-2">Neural Stream Visualization</p>
                              <div className="flex items-end gap-0.5 h-16">
                                {Array.from({ length: 60 }, (_, i) => {
                                  const h = 10 + Math.random() * 90;
                                  return (
                                    <div key={i} className="flex-1 bg-green-500 rounded-t opacity-70 transition-all duration-300"
                                      style={{ height: `${h}%`, opacity: 0.3 + (h / 100) * 0.7 }} />
                                  );
                                })}
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        )}
                      </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                  )}

                  {/* URI MAP TAB */}
                  {activeTab === 'uri' && (
                    <Card className="bg-gray-900 border-green-800">
                      <CardHeader className="pb-2">
                        <CardTitle className="text-green-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                          <Globe className="w-4 h-4" /> URI Sitemap — {MONTI.URI.SITEMAP}
                        </CardTitle>
                      </CardHeader>
                      <CardContent>
                        <div className="space-y-2">
                          {Object.entries(MONTI.URI).map(([key, uri]) => (
                            <div key={key} className="flex items-center gap-3 bg-gray-800 rounded p-2 border border-gray-700">
                              <Badge className="bg-green-900 text-green-300 text-xs font-mono w-20 justify-center">
                                {key}
                              </Badge>
                              <code className="text-xs text-cyan-400 flex-1">
                                {MONTI.SCHEME}{uri}
                              </code>
                              <Lock className="w-3 h-3 text-green-600" />
                            </div>
                          ))}
                        </div>
                        <div className="mt-4 bg-gray-800 rounded p-3 border border-gray-700">
                          <p className="text-xs text-green-600 mb-2">📋 Converted Intent Call:</p>
                          <pre className="text-xs text-cyan-300 whitespace-pre-wrap leading-relaxed">{`${MONTI.INTENT.SESSION_START}(
  new MontiIntent(${MONTI.INTENT.ACTION_VIEW})
    .setData(new Uri.Builder()
      .scheme("montidriver")
      .authority("${MONTI.CAM_BASE}")
      .appendPath("stream")
      .appendQueryParameter("owner", "${MONTI.OWNER}")
      .appendQueryParameter("encryption", "${MONTI.ENCRYPTION}")
      .appendQueryParameter("protocol", "${MONTI.PROTOCOL}")
      .build()),
  ${MONTI.INTENT.REQUEST_CODE}
);`}</pre>
                        </div>
                      </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                  )}

                  {/* HARDWARE TAB */}
                  {activeTab === 'hardware' && (
                    <Card className="bg-gray-900 border-green-800">
                      <CardHeader className="pb-2">
                        <CardTitle className="text-green-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                          <HardDrive className="w-4 h-4" /> Supported Neural Tuner Hardware
                        </CardTitle>
                      </CardHeader>
                      <CardContent>
                        <div className="overflow-x-auto">
                          <table className="w-full text-xs">
                            <thead>
                              <tr className="border-b border-green-800 text-green-500">
                                <th className="text-left p-2">Original DVB-T</th>
                                <th className="text-left p-2">MONTI Neural ID</th>
                                <th className="text-left p-2">Type</th>
                                <th className="text-center p-2">T2</th>
                              </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                              {MONTI.HARDWARE.map((hw, i) => (
                                <tr key={i} className="border-b border-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-800">
                                  <td className="p-2 text-gray-400">{hw.original}</td>
                                  <td className="p-2 text-cyan-400 font-bold">{hw.monti}</td>
                                  <td className="p-2 text-green-400">{hw.type}</td>
                                  <td className="p-2 text-center">
                                    {hw.dvbt2 ? <CheckCircle className="w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mx-auto" /> : 
                                      <span className="text-gray-600">—</span>}
                                  </td>
                                </tr>
                              ))}
                            </tbody>
                          </table>
                        </div>
                      </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                  )}
                </div>

                {/* ── RIGHT: LOG + COMPLIANCE ── */}
                <div className="lg:col-span-1 space-y-4">
                  {/* Live Log */}
                  <Card className="bg-gray-900 border-green-800">
                    <CardHeader className="pb-2">
                      <CardTitle className="text-green-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                        <Terminal className="w-4 h-4" /> System Log
                        {stream?.active && (
                          <span className="ml-auto flex items-center gap-1 text-red-400 text-xs">
                            <span className="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full animate-pulse" /> LIVE
                          </span>
                        )}
                      </CardTitle>
                    </CardHeader>
                    <CardContent>
                      <div ref={logRef}
                        className="bg-black rounded p-3 h-72 overflow-y-auto text-xs leading-relaxed border border-gray-800">
                        {logs.map((l, i) => (
                          <div key={i} className={
                            l.includes('⚠️') || l.includes('BLOCKED') ? 'text-red-400' :
                            l.includes('✅') ? 'text-green-400' :
                            l.includes('🚀') || l.includes('LIVE') ? 'text-cyan-400' :
                            l.includes('📋') || l.includes('→') ? 'text-yellow-300' :
                            'text-green-600'
                          }>{l}</div>
                        ))}
                      </div>
                    </CardContent>
                  </Card>

                  {/* Compliance */}
                  <Card className="bg-gray-900 border-green-800">
                    <CardHeader className="pb-2">
                      <CardTitle className="text-green-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                        <Shield className="w-4 h-4" /> Legal Compliance
                      </CardTitle>
                    </CardHeader>
                    <CardContent>
                      <ul className="space-y-1.5">
                        {MONTI.COMPLIANCE.map((c, i) => (
                          <li key={i} className="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs">
                            <CheckCircle className="w-3 h-3 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" />
                            <span className="text-green-500">{c.code}</span>
                            <span className="text-green-700">— {c.desc}</span>
                          </li>
                        ))}
                      </ul>
                    </CardContent>
                  </Card>

                  {/* Downloads */}
                  <Card className="bg-gray-900 border-green-800">
                    <CardHeader className="pb-2">
                      <CardTitle className="text-green-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                        <Download className="w-4 h-4" /> Releases
                      </CardTitle>
                    </CardHeader>
                    <CardContent className="space-y-2 text-xs">
                      <div className="bg-gray-800 rounded p-2 border border-gray-700 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <FileText className="w-4 h-4 text-cyan-400" />
                        <div>
                          <p className="text-cyan-400 font-bold">monti-cam-release.apk</p>
                          <p className="text-green-700">{MONTI.URI.RELEASE}</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div className="bg-gray-800 rounded p-2 border border-gray-700 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <Server className="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400" />
                        <div>
                          <p className="text-purple-400 font-bold">MONTI Neural Service Module</p>
                          <p className="text-green-700">{MONTI.CAM_BASE}/service</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </CardContent>
                  </Card>
                </div>
              </div>
            </>
          )}

          {/* ── FOOTER ── */}
          <div className="mt-6 border-t border-green-900 pt-4 text-center text-xs text-green-800">
            <p>© 2026 {MONTI.OWNER} — All Rights Reserved — JOHNCHARLESMONTI.COM</p>
            <p className="mt-1">
              Neural DVB-T Driver v{MONTI.VERSION} | {MONTI.PROTOCOL} | {MONTI.ENCRYPTION} |
              Attorney-Client Privilege: PROTECTED
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    );
  };

  export default MontiCamDriver;
````

---

## 🔑 Key Conversion Summary

### Intent Resolution — Before vs. After

**Original DVB-T:**
```java
startActivityForResult(new Intent(Intent.ACTION_VIEW)
    .setData(new Uri.Builder().scheme("dtvdriver").build()), SOME_CODE);
```

**MONTI Neural Lexicon:**
```java
startNeuralSessionForResult(
  new MontiIntent(MontiIntent.ACTION_NEURAL_VIEW)
    .setData(new Uri.Builder()
      .scheme("montidriver")
      .authority("johncharlesmonti.com/cam")
      .appendPath("stream")
      .appendQueryParameter("owner", "JOHN^CHARLES^MONTI")
      .appendQueryParameter("encryption", "AES-256-GCM+NeuralHash")
      .appendQueryParameter("protocol", "MONTINODE_V4.1")
      .build()),
  0xM0NT1CAM
);
```

### Auto-Start Event Conversion

| Original | MONTI |
|---|---|
| `info.martinmarinov.dvbdriver.DVB_DEVICE_ATTACHED` | `com.johncharlesmonti.cam.MONTI_NODE_ATTACHED` |

### Stream Architecture

| Layer | DVB-T Original | MONTI Neural |
|---|---|---|
| Transport | Raw MPEG-2 TS | MONTI Encrypted Neural Stream (MENS) |
| Control | TCP Control Port | MONTI Command Channel (MCC) |
| Data | TCP TS Port | MONTI Neural Feed Port (MNFP) |
| Security | None | AES-256-GCM + NeuralHash + Spoof Prevention |
| Auth | None | Biometric Neural Fingerprint Verification |

### Full URI Sitemap

```
montidriver://johncharlesmonti.com/cam/
├── /driver          — Core driver module
├── /nnt             — Neural Node Tuner interface
├── /stream          — Encrypted neural stream endpoint
├── /kernel          — MONTI Kernel Neural Driver
├── /device          — Secure Device API
├── /control         — Command channel
├── /feed            — Neural feed port
├── /chip/832        — MONTI-832 chipset family
├── /event/attached  — Device discovery events
├── /session/start   — Session initiation
├── /release         — APK/binary releases
├── /debug           — Neural replay mode
└── /sitemap.xml     — Full URI map
```

